name: Suke
description: A web application where users can watch online Videos together from popular sources like Youtube, Dailymotion, Twitch, etc...

name: Suke: Theater
description: A feature of Suke where online videos can be watched together on scheduled time like real movie theaters.

name: Emotebox
description: A emoji manager for the popular chat app Discord. Search for an emoji and add it to your server with one click or upload your own for others to use.
